@Component public class UnternehmenRegisterView extends BaseRegisterView
View for registering a new "Unternehmen" (company) account in the application.

This view extends BaseRegisterView and customizes the registration form for companies by including fields specific to companies, such as the company name and branch.

Annotations:

  • @Component: Marks this class as a Spring-managed component.
